Keller Williams Big Bear Lake Arrowhead

data.description: This adorable Big Bear City property is on a quiet street, with front and back decks, a fenced back yard, and is set back from the street for privacy. This home has a brick fireplace, a nook off the living room that looks out on the front deck, tree, and neighborhood, open kitchen with breakfast bar, range set into the peninsula, and a vented range hood. The main floor also has a bedroom with access to the back yard, and a 3/4 bath. Upstairs, the bright and airy ensuite has a paneled feature wall, lots of windows, a walk-in closet, and a full bath! The antler light fixtures, knotty pine T&G ceiling and accent walls, and the cozy fireplace on the main floor give the home a cabiney, yet modern feel. The stackable washer and dryer, as well as the range and refrigerator, are included in the sale. A few blocks from scenic Hwy 38, Maple Hills hiking trails, public transit, and convenience store, as well as a short drive to activities, slopes, lake, dining and events, this home could make a great full-time residence, mountain getaway, or investment.
